Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

################################################################################
##   Gmail                                                                    ##
################################################################################

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User chris@ctoomey.com
PassCmd "keychain-password chris@ctoomey.com"
UseIMAPS yes

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail-INBOX
Master :gmail-remote:INBOX
Slave :gmail-local:INBOX

Channel gmail-Drafts
Master :gmail-remote:[Gmail]/Drafts
Slave :gmail-local:Drafts

Channel gmail-Sent
Master ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:Sent

Channel gmail-Archive
Master ":gmail-remote:[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:Archive

Channel gmail-Trash
Master :gmail-remote:[Gmail]/Trash
Slave :gmail-local:Trash

Channel gmail-Followup
Master :gmail-remote:[Mailbox]/follow-up
Slave :gmail-local:Followup

Channel gmail-Capture
Master :gmail-remote:capture
Slave :gmail-local:Capture

Group gmail
Channel gmail-INBOX
Channel gmail-Drafts
Channel gmail-Sent
Channel gmail-Trash
Channel gmail-Followup
Channel gmail-Capture

